Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.74,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好了 提摩西\N{\rOriginal Text}All right, Timothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.39,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好戲上場了 兄弟\N{\rOriginal Text}It is go time, brother. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.57,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我需要五分鐘後上樓\N{\rOriginal Text}Now, I need to be upstairs in five--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:11.92,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,改成三分鐘\N{\rOriginal Text}make that three-minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:13.05,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思 這該死的芯片\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm sorry, it's this darn chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:14.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不知道是要刷一下\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't know whether to-to swipe it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.10,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,碰一下 還是感應一下 所以\N{\rOriginal Text}or tap it or wave it. Which means I need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:17.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我需要知道你們願意支付的上限\N{\rOriginal Text}the ceiling, okay? The absolute ceiling that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:18.88,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,最高的價格\N{\rOriginal Text}your guys are willing to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思 這樣吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Sorry. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我付現金\N{\rOriginal Text}I'll just get cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.80,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她的賬我結 給我來個美式中杯\N{\rOriginal Text}Um, hers is on me. I'll take a tall drip,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:26.50,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,零錢不用找了 23 好的\N{\rOriginal Text}and you can keep the change. 23, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.07,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那我要在19成交\N{\rOriginal Text}Which means I'm gonna close at 19,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.15,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,等他們準備跳單時 你記得提醒你老闆\N{\rOriginal Text}so you remind your bosses how much I saved them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:31.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我幫他們節省了多少錢\N{\rOriginal Text}when they try to fight my bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:36.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,今天真是一個美好的開始\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, isn't that a nice way to start the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.12,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,別人還說這世界要完蛋了\N{\rOriginal Text}And they say the world is going to poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.54,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我幫你\N{\rOriginal Text}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.37,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,今天的好心人真多\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh. Well, this is the day of kind gestures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.29,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,感激不盡\N{\rOriginal Text}I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:17.55,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我送你一個\N{\rOriginal Text}May I offer you one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我奶奶超喜歡這些\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh. My grandma loves these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這是生物本能\N{\rOriginal Text}It's biological.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,到了一定年紀 我們就開始買這些\N{\rOriginal Text}We hit a certain age and we start buying 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.39,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,相信我 我也想拒絕的\N{\rOriginal Text}Believe you me, I tried to resist,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可是到了65以後 不知不覺地\N{\rOriginal Text}and then I turned 65, and next thing I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,就發現自己站在好多超市裏\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm standing smack-dab in the middle of a Costco
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.18,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,拿著個四磅重的袋子\N{\rOriginal Text}with a four-pound bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:36.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,21樓 謝謝\N{\rOriginal Text}Uh, 21st floor, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.40,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可能就是這樣\N{\rOriginal Text}I guess that's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:43.36,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,一生中很多時刻 我們都成了\N{\rOriginal Text}Lots of times in life, we become exactly who
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:45.54,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,別人期望我們成為的樣子\N{\rOriginal Text}people expect us to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:46.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\rOriginal Text}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:48.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\rOriginal Text}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.76,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,克裏斯汀 幫我開下門 我沒手開\N{\rOriginal Text}Kristine, can you buzz me in? Hands are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.01,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你好 週一快樂\N{\rOriginal Text}Hello and happy Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.27,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,開始之前\N{\rOriginal Text}Before we dive in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.54,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,向你們這些大都會球迷 致以深切哀悼\N{\rOriginal Text}my deep condolences to all you Mets fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:31.97,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好吧 那真是\N{\rOriginal Text}All right, that's... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.11,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對 我聽說你們很多人去看了比賽\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, I heard a bunch of you went to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.72,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,團建 為了團隊氣氛\N{\rOriginal Text}Team building. It's good for morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.85,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,向大家表明 即使我現在成了權益合夥人\N{\rOriginal Text}Shows that even though I'm an equity partner now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我還是跟你們一樣\N{\rOriginal Text}I am still one of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,打心眼兒裏是個普通合夥人\N{\rOriginal Text}a regular partner at heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.42,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不談薪水的話\N{\rOriginal Text}if not in salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rOriginal Text}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.64,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,奧林匹亞 我聽說哈里斯的民事訴訟\N{\rOriginal Text}Olympia, I heard you got a $2 million offer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.51,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你拿到了200萬的和解報價\N{\rOriginal Text}to settle the Harris civil action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.03,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是的 我拒絕了 庭審定在\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, and I rejected it. That trial is slated to start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.91,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,明天 無論如何 都不能進入庭審\N{\rOriginal Text}tomorrow, and you cannot go to trial under any circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:54.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我會達成交易的\N{\rOriginal Text}And I will be closing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.87,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可是兩百萬遠遠不夠 伊利亞\N{\rOriginal Text}but $2 million is not enough, Elijah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.17,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德·哈里斯失去了26年的時光\N{\rOriginal Text}Raymond Harris lost 26 years of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我覺得最少得四百萬\N{\rOriginal Text}I need $4 million, minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.35,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,如果我能找到確鑿證據\N{\rOriginal Text}20 if I can just find the smoking gun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.22,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,證明警察腐敗 那就得要兩千萬\N{\rOriginal Text}to prove that there was police corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你都找了六個月了\N{\rOriginal Text}You've been looking for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:09.01,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,沒有給我分配合適的資源\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I haven't been allocated the proper resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.66,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,朱利安 給你配了兩個\N{\rOriginal Text}Julian. You have two associates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.58,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,初級律師 24小時任你差遭\N{\rOriginal Text}working around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.71,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,兩個初級律師 抵不上一個普通律師\N{\rOriginal Text}Two very junior associates who equal one mediocre associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.37,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你就是這麼鼓舞士氣的\N{\rOriginal Text}Is that your way of building morale?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,聽著 我可能有了新線索\N{\rOriginal Text}Look, I might have a new lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那個妓女的素描\N{\rOriginal Text}A sketch of the prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,結束了 奧林匹亞\N{\rOriginal Text}It's over, Olympia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,結了這個案子\N{\rOriginal Text}close the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.03,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,朱利安\N{\rOriginal Text}Julian,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,說說皮搏迪的情況\N{\rOriginal Text}talk to me about Peabody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.51,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們昨晚私下聊了\N{\rOriginal Text}We back-channeled last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.99,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他們把價格提到一千九百萬\N{\rOriginal Text}and I got them up to $19 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,實際上 你們可以從\N{\rOriginal Text}Actually, you can get
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:35.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,皮博迪那裏要到更多\N{\rOriginal Text}quite a bit more out of Peabody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.74,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你哪位\N{\rOriginal Text}Uh, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.74,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我有點激動得忘乎所以了\N{\rOriginal Text}Sorry, I got a little ahead of myself in my excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.83,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,非正式場合 叫我瑪蒂\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm Matty, informally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.57,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,正式場合叫我瑪德琳·馬特洛克\N{\rOriginal Text}Formally Madeline Matlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.53,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對 跟之前電視劇裏的馬特洛克同名\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, Matlock like the old TV show,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:52.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,1984年到1992年期間 聽到的全是這個\N{\rOriginal Text}which was all I heard between 1984 and 1992.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:56.06,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你跟馬特洛克一樣是個律師 你跟馬特洛克一樣是個律師\N{\rOriginal Text}"You're a lawyer like Matlock. You're a lawyer like Matlock."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.93,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,每次我都要糾正他們\N{\rOriginal Text}And every time I'd correct 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.67,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不對 他是假律師\N{\rOriginal Text}"No, he's just pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我可是真律師\N{\rOriginal Text}You know, I'm a real lawyer."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.72,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可是你們懂的 抗議次數多了\N{\rOriginal Text}But, you know, you can only protest so much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.55,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,別人就會覺得你小題大做 心胸狹隘\N{\rOriginal Text}before you sound like you got a big old pole up your heinie,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.55,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,聽以 我也就不糾結了\N{\rOriginal Text}so I just let 'em have it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,只是回答 對 對 對\N{\rOriginal Text}and I just said, "Yeah, well, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.42,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我跟馬特洛克一樣 是律師\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm a lawyer just like Matlock."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.99,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,您在哪家律所工作\N{\rOriginal Text}A lawyer working for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.69,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,希望是在這裏\N{\rOriginal Text}You, hopefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.69,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們要招初級律師\N{\rOriginal Text}You have an associate position open,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,要想找個面試機會真難得\N{\rOriginal Text}and it's been really hard to get an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.56,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我差點以為是因為我太老了\N{\rOriginal Text}And I almost think it's 'cause of my age,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:27.17,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但是 這樣就違背了反歧視規定\N{\rOriginal Text}but that'd be violating discriminatory protections.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,關鍵是 我必須想辦法\N{\rOriginal Text}The point is, I just had to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,打破這種困境\N{\rOriginal Text}a way to break through the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你的確為自己贏得了面試機會\N{\rOriginal Text}I think you definitely earned yourself an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.44,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,感謝您的認可\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, thank you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.88,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可我要的不是面試\N{\rOriginal Text}but I don't want an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:37.97,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而是工作\N{\rOriginal Text}I want a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.97,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,提醒一下\N{\rOriginal Text}And as a reminder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.80,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我很清楚皮博迪願意\N{\rOriginal Text}I do know the number that Peabody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.37,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,支付和解金\N{\rOriginal Text}is willing to pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.85,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而且比一千九百萬高一點兒\N{\rOriginal Text}and it is significantly higher than $19 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:49.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,當然 也不能對皮博迪漫天要價\N{\rOriginal Text}Course, I wouldn't overplay my hand with Peabody either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:52.33,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我一向認為 談判既是一門藝術\N{\rOriginal Text}I always say negotiations are an art
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,也是一個陷阱\N{\rOriginal Text}and a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.86,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那就避開陷阱 你怎麼知道報價的\N{\rOriginal Text}Let's avoid traps, then. How do you know the number?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.47,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你看女人到了我這個年紀\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, you see, there's this funny thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,就有一個有趣的現象\N{\rOriginal Text}that happens when women age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.60,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好像沒人會注意到我們\N{\rOriginal Text}We become damn near invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:04.86,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我不是在抱怨\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, not that I'm complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.30,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我也有過高光時刻\N{\rOriginal Text}I had my moment in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:11.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,再說了 無人警惕是致勝的法寶\N{\rOriginal Text}Plus it's useful because nobody sees us coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:14.40,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我就是這樣騙過你們保安的\N{\rOriginal Text}That's how I got through your security.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.05,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好幾次了\N{\rOriginal Text}Several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我也是這樣知道\N{\rOriginal Text}And it's also how I knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.66,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,皮博迪的律師 在8點15到25之間\N{\rOriginal Text}Peabody's counsel grabs coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,買咖啡時 向他的客戶匯報情況的\N{\rOriginal Text}and updates his client between 8:15 and 8:25.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:23.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對方給價多少\N{\rOriginal Text}What's the number?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.45,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我被錄用了嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Am I hired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.54,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所有人錄用前 都有兩周的試用期\N{\rOriginal Text}No one is hired without a two-week trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.50,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他們的上限是多少\N{\rOriginal Text}What's their ceiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.20,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,兩千三百萬\N{\rOriginal Text}$23 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.28,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,意思是我剛剛替你們\N{\rOriginal Text}Which means I just made you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.98,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,賺了四百萬\N{\rOriginal Text}$4 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.20,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,還需要我試用兩周嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Do I still need a two-week trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.46,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.07,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那好吧 我就從今天開始\N{\rOriginal Text}All right, fine. I'll start today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:44.25,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,說說看 馬特洛克女士\N{\rOriginal Text}Tell me, Ms. Matlock,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.43,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼想在我們律所工作\N{\rOriginal Text}why do you want to work at my firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.30,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,人生中總有些時候\N{\rOriginal Text}There's a time in life when you make decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是基於自己的對錯觀做決定\N{\rOriginal Text}based on what you think is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.05,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,也有一些時候 基於自己的經濟狀況做決定\N{\rOriginal Text}and there's a time when you make decisions based on money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:58.44,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我一輩子都是基於我認為的正確做事\N{\rOriginal Text}I did what was right all my life, and now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.22,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,現在我就想多掙錢\N{\rOriginal Text}I need to make it rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.23,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,給我派個案子\N{\rOriginal Text}so point me to a case
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.27,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,讓我工作吧\N{\rOriginal Text}and put me to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.67,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她確實要求加派人手\N{\rOriginal Text}She did ask for extra resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們結識的時機好像不太好\N{\rOriginal Text}We seem to have gotten off on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:18.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這走得也太快了\N{\rOriginal Text}Wow, that is quite the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我只想真正派上用場\N{\rOriginal Text}Um, I just truly want to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.46,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,無論你需要什麼 能力\N{\rOriginal Text}Anything you need. Competence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我需要基本的能力\N{\rOriginal Text}I need basic competence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.12,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你上一次從事法律工作是什麼時候\N{\rOriginal Text}When was the last time you practiced law?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.03,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那是1991年\N{\rOriginal Text}Um, well, that was in 1991.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.73,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我知道 時隔30年肯定有困難\N{\rOriginal Text}And I understand 30 years can seem challenging,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.43,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但是我向你保證 我基本上時時關注\N{\rOriginal Text}but I assure you, I have remained pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,法律進展\N{\rOriginal Text}nearly up to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,基本上 還是差不多\N{\rOriginal Text}"Pretty nearly" or "almost sorta"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,讓我向你證明\N{\rOriginal Text}Just let me prove that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,告訴我 要怎麼做\N{\rOriginal Text}I can be useful. Tell me how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那就在感恩節幫幫我吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Get me all of Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.53,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我沒聽懂\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm sorry, I'm not following.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.53,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我一小時收費一千二 去找一個\N{\rOriginal Text}I charge $1,200 an hour, so clear that up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.23,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你負擔得起的人 給你解釋吧\N{\rOriginal Text}with somebody whose time you can afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.97,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們倆有消息嗎 還 沒有\N{\rOriginal Text}You two, anything? Nothing, no, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.67,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,記得我說過的嗎 回答不要這麼囉嗦\N{\rOriginal Text}Remember what we talked about? That should have been one word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.89,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好了 電話隨時可能進來\N{\rOriginal Text}Now, the call's coming in any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,去會議室見我\N{\rOriginal Text}Meet me in the conference room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.72,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,帶上這位新律師\N{\rOriginal Text}and bring the new lawyer with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.86,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,瑪德琳·馬特洛克\N{\rOriginal Text}Madeline Matlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.60,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,跟那個電視節目同名\N{\rOriginal Text}Like the TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:09.73,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,什麼節目\N{\rOriginal Text}What TV show?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.95,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 你們可以叫我瑪蒂\N{\rOriginal Text}Exactly. You can call me Matty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.78,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,第一天上班\N{\rOriginal Text}First day on the job,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好激動加入這個團隊\N{\rOriginal Text}thrilled to be part of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.82,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不要 這等於是噩夢\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, no. This is gonna be a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.43,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,友善點 友善\N{\rOriginal Text}Be nice. Nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,別叫我友善 我需要資深合夥人的培訓\N{\rOriginal Text}Don't tell me to be nice. I need to be trained by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不是資深老年人\N{\rOriginal Text}senior partners, not senior citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:23.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,天哪 無意冒犯 佩利·梅森\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, God. No offense, Perry Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.74,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是馬特洛克 就算你說無意冒犯\N{\rOriginal Text}Ha, Matlock. You know, if you say "no offense,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.66,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不代表這就有禮貌了 我們被降到\N{\rOriginal Text}it doesn't make it any less rude. We just got demoted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.23,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,第三檔了 比利\N{\rOriginal Text}to a third, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,替莎拉說句話\N{\rOriginal Text}In Sarah's defense, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.80,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她就是脾氣暴躁\N{\rOriginal Text}she's a raging bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她怎麼這麼火爆\N{\rOriginal Text}Why is she so pissy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.93,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,沒有私生活\N{\rOriginal Text}No social life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.76,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,再加上她野心勃勃\N{\rOriginal Text}And plus she's wildly ambitious,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們在這個案子上 花費了六個月時間\N{\rOriginal Text}and we've been working on this case for six months now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:42.11,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而奧林匹亞還是不知道我們倆的名字 她只說 你們倆\N{\rOriginal Text}and Olympia still calls us "youtwo." One word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.07,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以 你加入的不算是什麼精英團隊\N{\rOriginal Text}So, yeah, you're not exactly joining the A-team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,又是個你沒聽說過的電視節目名稱\N{\rOriginal Text}Another old TV show you never heard of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.64,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我和祖母看過那些電視劇\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, my abuela and I watched telenovelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.29,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你知道那些劇嗎 不知道\N{\rOriginal Text}You know any of those? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.90,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,也正常\N{\rOriginal Text}That's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.38,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,趁我還沒忘\N{\rOriginal Text}Hey, before I forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.56,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,奧林匹亞說要我給她感恩節\N{\rOriginal Text}Olympia mentioned I should get her Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.65,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你聽明白她什麼意思嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}You any idea what she's talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她可能是指監護權\N{\rOriginal Text}Uh, probably a custody thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.48,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,聽說他們的離婚已經鐵板釘釘\N{\rOriginal Text}Word is, their divorce is almost finalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.83,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對了 頂級零食點在這裏\N{\rOriginal Text}FYI, top snack destination here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.92,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,咸味甜味全都有\N{\rOriginal Text}You've got salty, you've got sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,要是你想哭 後面還有天井\N{\rOriginal Text}you've got access to the back patio in case you need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,申明一下 我想吃咸的\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, for the record, I'm salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.40,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,希望我不至於哭吧\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm hoping I won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.14,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你剛才說他們的離婚\N{\rOriginal Text}You said "their divorce."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.36,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,奧林匹亞跟誰離婚\N{\rOriginal Text}Who's Olympia divorcing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.54,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,朱利安\N{\rOriginal Text}Julian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,跟她吵架的那位\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, the guy she was arguing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.80,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,把它歸為 我永遠不會摻和的事\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, file that under "Things I'm never gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,絕對 不可能 永遠 不會\N{\rOriginal Text}get involved with, no way, nohow, no, sirree, Bob."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:26.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我要用老辦法贏得她的信任\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm gonna win her over the old-fashioned way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.46,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,跟我說說案情吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Catch me up on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:32.20,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好 雷蒙德·哈里斯因多起謀殺強姦罪\N{\rOriginal Text}Yep. Raymond Harris spent 26 years in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.60,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,判刑入獄26年\N{\rOriginal Text}as a convicted serial murderer/rapist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.51,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可是最近的DNA證據 洗清了他的罪名\N{\rOriginal Text}but was recently exonerated through DNA evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.64,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那時候的警局 水渾得不行\N{\rOriginal Text}Now, the police department was definitely dirty back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.21,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,各種不當行為 但是\N{\rOriginal Text}tons of misconduct, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.82,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,想要給他爭取到應得的賠償\N{\rOriginal Text}in order to get the payout that he deserves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們必須找到確鑿的證據\N{\rOriginal Text}we-we need to find the smoking gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:46.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家覺得一定能找到呢\N{\rOriginal Text}Why is everybody so sure there is one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:48.52,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,因為我們一個線人從他已故的\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, because we got a tip from a guy who got a tip
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.35,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,退休跟警察叔叔那裏 得到了線報\N{\rOriginal Text}from his dead uncle who was a retired cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.70,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,天啊 是的\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, Lord. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,總之 在雷蒙德被拘期間\N{\rOriginal Text}Anyway, apparently a prostitute escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:57.01,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,有個妓女又遭遇了類似襲擊 長襪被纏在脖子上\N{\rOriginal Text}a really similar attack while Raymond was still in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.10,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,完全遵循之前的模式 但她逃了出來\N{\rOriginal Text}Stocking around the neck, the whole nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,據說 她去警局報案了\N{\rOriginal Text}Word is, she went down to the station to file a report,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,只不過沒記錄\N{\rOriginal Text}only there's no record of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.97,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,也就是說 如果真有 也被掩蓋了\N{\rOriginal Text}which means if it exists, it was buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.58,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我猜你應該找不到26年前\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I'm guessing you can't find the prostitute
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:07.89,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那個妓女了\N{\rOriginal Text}from 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.33,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,連她名字都不知道\N{\rOriginal Text}Don't know her name,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.07,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是生是死 就更不知情了\N{\rOriginal Text}much less if she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這世界上可是有很多隱形人的\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, there's a lot of invisible people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.55,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,在合夥人會議上\N{\rOriginal Text}In the partners' meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,奧林匹亞提到過素描\N{\rOriginal Text}Olympia said something about a sketch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.25,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這很複雜\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, that's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.95,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但抱歉問一下\N{\rOriginal Text}Uh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.47,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼加入合夥人會議的\N{\rOriginal Text}How-how did you get into the partners' meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.47,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這說來話長了\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, that's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,下次我們一起吃咸的 我再告訴你\N{\rOriginal Text}I'll tell you about it next time we share something salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.87,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,還有其他信息要告訴我嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Is there anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,能博得奧林園亞歡心的\N{\rOriginal Text}I need to know to get on Olympia's good side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,千萬別告訴委託人你的看法\N{\rOriginal Text}Never give your opinion to a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.79,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,讓她來說\N{\rOriginal Text}Leave that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.40,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你好 雷蒙德 喬丹\N{\rOriginal Text}Hello, Raymond, Jordan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.92,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們還有另一位律師的加入\N{\rOriginal Text}Got one more lawyer as we bring this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.45,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,請說出你的名字\N{\rOriginal Text}Please state your name
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.80,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,以及你是否跟\N{\rOriginal Text}and whether you've ever had
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.58,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,警察局或我父親的案子\N{\rOriginal Text}any affiliation with the police department
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.32,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,有過直接或間接的關係\N{\rOriginal Text}or with my father's case, either directly or tangentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.45,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,喬丹喜歡把一切錄下來\N{\rOriginal Text}Jordan likes to record everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.67,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我不是喜歡錄\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't like to record everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.76,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我是不得不錄\N{\rOriginal Text}I have to record everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.89,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這樣才能追責\N{\rOriginal Text}To keep people accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:57.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我父親因為謊言被關了26年\N{\rOriginal Text}My father was locked up for 26 years because people lied,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.42,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以 如果有人在這裏撒謊\N{\rOriginal Text}so, if it happens in this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.90,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我都有記錄\N{\rOriginal Text}I have a record.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\rOriginal Text}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.69,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\rOriginal Text}Apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.43,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,瑪德琳·馬特洛克\N{\rOriginal Text}Madeline Matlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.21,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我和警察局沒有任何關係\N{\rOriginal Text}I have no affiliation with the police department
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.65,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,從來沒有過\N{\rOriginal Text}and never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.57,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了\N{\rOriginal Text}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.05,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了\N{\rOriginal Text}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他們開出了最後的和解協議\N{\rOriginal Text}The final settlement offer came in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:24.88,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是24萬1280美元\N{\rOriginal Text}and it's $241,280,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.40,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,在這個條件下 我必須問一下\N{\rOriginal Text}and at this point I have to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:27.45,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們要不要和解\N{\rOriginal Text}if you want to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.45,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,什麼 當初200萬\N{\rOriginal Text}What? We didn't settle
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.19,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們都沒和解\N{\rOriginal Text}for $2 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你憑什麼覺得 我們會接受20萬\N{\rOriginal Text}What the hell makes you think we'd settle for $200,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.19,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\rOriginal Text}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不 對不起\N{\rOriginal Text}No, no. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.81,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你不必道歉\N{\rOriginal Text}You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但我不明白 究竟出什麼事了\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay, I don't understand. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.38,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,庭審就在明天\N{\rOriginal Text}But the trial starts tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.12,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,事情有了些變數\N{\rOriginal Text}and something changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他們覺得我們的案子站不住腳\N{\rOriginal Text}They don't feel like we can make our case anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.82,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我很擔心\N{\rOriginal Text}and I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.47,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,沒有確鑿的證據\N{\rOriginal Text}Without the smoking gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.99,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,再加上你父親之前的犯罪記錄\N{\rOriginal Text}given your father's prior criminal history
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:54.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,以及他曾對罪行供認不諱\N{\rOriginal Text}and the fact that he confessed to the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.35,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我是屈打成招\N{\rOriginal Text}Under duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我後來翻供了 我知道\N{\rOriginal Text}I took it back. -I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但一開始的認罪 就意味著政府\N{\rOriginal Text}But that initial confession means that the city
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.53,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,沒有義務付你一分一毫\N{\rOriginal Text}is not obligated to pay you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:06.23,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對不起 雷蒙德 我們\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm sorry, Raymond, we've just--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們沒時間了\N{\rOriginal Text}we've run out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.01,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以 你現在\N{\rOriginal Text}OLYMPIA [on recording]: So... you have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.93,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,面臨一個重大決定 雷蒙德\N{\rOriginal Text}a very big decision to make, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:16.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,還記得這個嗎 這是我們第一次會面的錄音\N{\rOriginal Text}Remember this? This is from our first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.76,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我經常聽\N{\rOriginal Text}I listen to it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們已經見了很多律師\N{\rOriginal Text}You've met with a lot of lawyers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我很想告訴你 怎樣選都不會錯\N{\rOriginal Text}and I'd like to say there's no wrong decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但你知道嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}but you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.81,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們確實會選錯\N{\rOriginal Text}There is a wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.33,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但這也意味著 你們還有正確的選擇\N{\rOriginal Text}But that also means there's a right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.25,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我就是那個正確的選擇\N{\rOriginal Text}And I am that right decision
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.43,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,因為我相信你 雷蒙德\N{\rOriginal Text}because I believe in you, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我在乎的點 在於這個腐敗的警察局\N{\rOriginal Text}And I care that this corrupt police department
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,偷走了你的未來\N{\rOriginal Text}stole your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:43.70,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,相信我 相信我吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Trust me. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.14,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你覺得呢\N{\rOriginal Text}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.93,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,呃\N{\rOriginal Text}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.19,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,說吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.71,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你要是有什麼意見 就說出來\N{\rOriginal Text}If you have an opinion, give it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:09.33,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他們的和解無異於羞辱 咱們上法庭吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Their offer's insulting. Go to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.20,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\rOriginal Text}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:15.56,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你說過你有辦法贏 找辦法吧\N{\rOriginal Text}You said you'd come through, so come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.39,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們覺得奧林園亞 會怪我勸他們庭審嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}You think Olympia's blaming me for going to trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可能不會 百分百會\N{\rOriginal Text}Probably not. A hundred percent yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我是說 我會的\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你是說 馬特洛克女士壓你一頭\N{\rOriginal Text}You're saying Ms. Matlock convinced them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,說服了他們\N{\rOriginal Text}and one-upped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.23,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她沒壓我一頭 我現在又有更多理由\N{\rOriginal Text}She didn't one-up me. Now I'm a step closer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.93,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,解雇她了\N{\rOriginal Text}to firing her for cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.06,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,坦白講 我也不想讓雷蒙德和解\N{\rOriginal Text}And frankly, I didn't want to convince Raymond to settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.06,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不像話 律所需要你回到\N{\rOriginal Text}Unacceptable. The firm needs you back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.19,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那些真正賺錢的案子上來\N{\rOriginal Text}on cases that actually make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我連續三年的計費都超過了\N{\rOriginal Text}And I billed more than any other junior partner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:46.46,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,其他初級合夥人\N{\rOriginal Text}for three straight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可你追了一個案子6個月都徒勞無功\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, hard to remember when you've been hunting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.85,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,之前的好感都敗光了\N{\rOriginal Text}goose eggs for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.29,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,因為我在幫咱們\N{\rOriginal Text}Because I'm trying to establish
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.72,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,開拓全新的收入源 沒一個人支持我\N{\rOriginal Text}a whole new revenue stream with no support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.25,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對方曾三次試圖更改庭審地點\N{\rOriginal Text}I fought off three separate attempts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.03,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,都被我擊敗了\N{\rOriginal Text}to have the venue changed by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:59.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,也就是說 整個陪審團都知道\N{\rOriginal Text}which means the whole jury pool knows that there has been
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.43,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,警察腐敗現象的嚴重\N{\rOriginal Text}extensive police corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.30,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,陪審團之所以知道 是因為\N{\rOriginal Text}And the whole jury pool knows that because I've
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.74,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我讓這事上了報紙\N{\rOriginal Text}kept the story in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:06.22,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以 之前政府才同意和解的\N{\rOriginal Text}Which is why the city was settling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,之前 是關鍵\N{\rOriginal Text}"Was" being the operative word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,太對了 那時我連個私家偵探\N{\rOriginal Text}Exactly. And without a private investigator
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.53,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,其至陪審團顧問都沒有\N{\rOriginal Text}or, at the very least, a jury consultant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.75,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,現在依然沒有\N{\rOriginal Text}I have no idea what changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.70,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,律所不想把錢投到無償案件上\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, the firm isn't gonna pump money into a pro bono case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.05,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,理想狀況下\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, ideally,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:20.75,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這不是無償案子 這只是一個試水案件\N{\rOriginal Text}this isn't pro bono. It's a test case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.28,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,奧林匹亞之前為大型製藥公司做辯護 搞得精疲力盡\N{\rOriginal Text}Olympia got burned out after defending Big Pharma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:26.50,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,大型製藥公司 他們有錢啊 我想去\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, Big Pharma, big money. That's where I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.15,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,對了 什麼叫試水案件\N{\rOriginal Text}So what do you mean this is a test case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.89,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,如果雷蒙德得到的賠償金\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, if Raymond gets a number
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,高於全國平均水平\N{\rOriginal Text}higher than the national average,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.24,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,律所就會從中抽成\N{\rOriginal Text}then the firm takes a cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.64,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以奧林匹亞一方面告訴他\N{\rOriginal Text}So Olympia's argument to him is that she can get
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.38,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,能幫他爭取更高的金額\N{\rOriginal Text}a much higher number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,一方面又告訴律所 追求社會正義\N{\rOriginal Text}And the argument to the firm is that social justice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.12,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,也能賺得真金白銀\N{\rOriginal Text}can mean real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.12,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,行善和賺錢可以兼得\N{\rOriginal Text}So you can do good and do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.47,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,總之 這是高尚的說法\N{\rOriginal Text}That's the noble version, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.21,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,不高尚的說法呢\N{\rOriginal Text}What's the non-noble version?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.56,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她在尋找一種將不幸變現的方法\N{\rOriginal Text}She's figuring out yet another way to monetize misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,因為她就是那麼天才\N{\rOriginal Text}because she's a freaking genius. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.61,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你馬上要成高級合夥人了\N{\rOriginal Text}You're coming up for senior partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,熟輕熟重 不需要我提醒你吧\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't have to remind you what's at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.48,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那你還提醒\N{\rOriginal Text}Then why are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.10,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,因為我仍舊是你公公\N{\rOriginal Text}Because I'm still your father-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.62,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,離婚手續馬上走完了\N{\rOriginal Text}The divorce is almost finalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.10,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你以為我在乎嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}You think I give a rat's ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:08.41,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,公公是個終生的身份\N{\rOriginal Text}Father-in-law is a lifetime position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.98,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我知道熟輕熟重\N{\rOriginal Text}I know what's at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.89,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我只是希望這條路能走通\N{\rOriginal Text}I just want this to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.50,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rOriginal Text}I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:18.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但如果走不通\N{\rOriginal Text}But if it doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.46,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你還要回來做公司訴訟的\N{\rOriginal Text}you're back on corporate litigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.42,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,明白嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.42,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,現在最重要也是我們\N{\rOriginal Text}So the biggest question
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.29,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,必須定下的事情\N{\rOriginal Text}we have to tackle is:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.38,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是要讓雷蒙德出庭嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}should Raymond be called to the stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.65,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,要是有個陪審團顧問就好了\N{\rOriginal Text}What we need is a jury consultant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:29.65,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以提前\N{\rOriginal Text}so that we can audition
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.04,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,排練一下雷蒙德的證詞\N{\rOriginal Text}Raymond's testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.87,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,看看模擬陪審團會反應如何\N{\rOriginal Text}see how the mock jury will respond to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:36.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但很不幸 我們請不起\N{\rOriginal Text}But unfortunately we can't afford that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.74,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以 你需要的是白牌貨\N{\rOriginal Text}So you need the off-brand model, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.96,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這麼說吧 甚至是免費贈品\N{\rOriginal Text}Or better yet, a freebie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,自從我消費降級後\N{\rOriginal Text}Which is what I'm always looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.79,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我也一直在找這些東西\N{\rOriginal Text}since my circumstances changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.01,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,舉個例子 我已經不買番茄醬了\N{\rOriginal Text}For instance, I stopped buying ketchup
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:48.14,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而是把在外面吃飯的番茄醬包\N{\rOriginal Text}and I started bringing ketchup packets home
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.19,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,帶回家\N{\rOriginal Text}every time I went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.98,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而這家律所一定有很多人\N{\rOriginal Text}And this firm definitely has a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.93,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,喜歡番茄醬\N{\rOriginal Text}who like ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,什麼 老頭子知道我們要往下推進了\N{\rOriginal Text}What? Senior knows we're moving forward
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他才是這裏的老大\N{\rOriginal Text}and he's the one in charge,
