Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,一個20多歲的亞洲女性\N{\rOriginal Text}a 20-something Asian woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.70,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,和兩個50多歲的白人女性嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}and two white ladies in their 50s?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你可以去秘書處\N{\rOriginal Text}Go to the secretaries,
