Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.31,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以 他們就是我們的免費番茄醬\N{\rOriginal Text}So they're our free ketchup packets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.70,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我們會根據陪審團的人口構成\N{\rOriginal Text}We'll match the demographics
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:30.58,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,找來相應的律所員工\N{\rOriginal Text}of the jury and preview Raymond's testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.75,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,然後一起預演雷蒙德的證詞\N{\rOriginal Text}with people who are already here on the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們三個 我們是可以分拆的\N{\rOriginal Text}And you three... You know, you can actually separate us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,噓\N{\rOriginal Text}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.50,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,去謝琳家把她的素描拿過來\N{\rOriginal Text}Go to Sherleen's and get her sketch. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,謝琳是誰 一個老妓女\N{\rOriginal Text}Who's Sherleen? An old ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.38,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她就是這麼叫自己的\N{\rOriginal Text}That's what she calls herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.77,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我有次稱她為 性工作長者 她還糾正我\N{\rOriginal Text}I said "aging prostitute" once and she corrected me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.51,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我是個老妓女 收到\N{\rOriginal Text}"I'm an old ho."Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我只是說\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm just saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.04,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,馬特吉弗說了一大段的番茄醬\N{\rOriginal Text}MacGyver does a whole ketchup monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:55.60,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,都沒被她閉嘴\N{\rOriginal Text}and she doesn't get shushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我叫馬特洛克\N{\rOriginal Text}It's-it's Matlock, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.17,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,因為那一長段番茄醬 說到點子上了\N{\rOriginal Text}Because the ketchup monologue was useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.52,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好了 別糾結了\N{\rOriginal Text}Get over yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.30,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,順便交代下 謝琳是個十足的瘋貨\N{\rOriginal Text}FYI, Sherleen's kind of a nutjob.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:03.78,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但她在街上工作了很久\N{\rOriginal Text}But she's worked the streets a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她說她對我們\N{\rOriginal Text}and she says that she remembers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.66,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,在找的那個妓女有印象\N{\rOriginal Text}the prostitute we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.88,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,除了不記得她名字 和任何有用的信息\N{\rOriginal Text}Just not her name. Or anything useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.36,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而且 莎拉\N{\rOriginal Text}And, Sarah... Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.75,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,小心眼兒\N{\rOriginal Text}So petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.01,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,她誰啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:16.27,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你好 我是瑪蒂 很高興認識你\N{\rOriginal Text}Hey, I'm Matty. It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.36,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你家真不錯哎\N{\rOriginal Text}Wow. I love your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.11,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,謝了 我自己佈置的\N{\rOriginal Text}Thanks, I did the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,那邊那個 可以很直觀的讓你有個瞭解\N{\rOriginal Text}That over there is a useful map.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你知道陰蒂在哪裏嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}You know where your clitoris is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,很多你這年紀的女人都不知道\N{\rOriginal Text}Lots of women your age don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:32.46,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我是肯定知道的 可我丈夫就不知道了\N{\rOriginal Text}I certainly do. Though my husband didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.86,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,而且我什麼都沒說過 想想看\N{\rOriginal Text}And I never said anything. Imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,38年我連句\N{\rOriginal Text}38 years and I never said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.04,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你能稍微往左一丁點\N{\rOriginal Text}"Could you just move a little to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,速度提一倍嗎 都沒說過\N{\rOriginal Text}and go twice as fast?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.00,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,當然了 他也沒跟我說過\N{\rOriginal Text}Course, he never told me he was sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他跟別人睡了 還染上了嚴重賭癮\N{\rOriginal Text}with other people and had a massive gambling problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:49.83,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,搞得我欠了一身債 所以算是扯平了吧\N{\rOriginal Text}which left me in debt, so I guess we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.44,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我喜歡她\N{\rOriginal Text}I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.18,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我也喜歡你\N{\rOriginal Text}I like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.84,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你幫我們\N{\rOriginal Text}Thanks for helping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:58.32,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我去找下那幅素描\N{\rOriginal Text}I'll go find the sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.36,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,慢慢找\N{\rOriginal Text}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.15,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這裏可欣賞的太多了\N{\rOriginal Text}Wow, there's so much to look at here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,顯然你過得很充實\N{\rOriginal Text}Clearly a life well-lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:10.02,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,我就不一樣了 挑錯男人了\N{\rOriginal Text}Not me. I picked the wrong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.11,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好 素描在這兒\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay, here's my sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.94,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,其實是幅畫\N{\rOriginal Text}Actually, it's a painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.34,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\rOriginal Text}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.64,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,用了很多橙色啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Lot of orange up top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:22.17,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,是她的髮色嗎 沒錯\N{\rOriginal Text}That's her hair color? Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.73,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,很混亂 對不對\N{\rOriginal Text}It's very chaotic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,毒品讓人混亂\N{\rOriginal Text}Drugs make people chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.26,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,確實\N{\rOriginal Text}They certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:28.39,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,你們有查過 一年內\N{\rOriginal Text}And you all ran the names
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:30.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,被謝琳畫過的\N{\rOriginal Text}of all the prostitutes arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.83,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所有妓女的名字嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}within the year by Sherleen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.09,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,當然了 整個蘭州地區的都查了\N{\rOriginal Text}Of course. In the whole tristate area.
