Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.79,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,指控的人嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}with narcotics charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.49,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,畢竟根據這副素描所示 我們這位\N{\rOriginal Text}Since our, uh, our prostitute here had
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.15,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,妓女有 混亂的毒品問題\N{\rOriginal Text}a "chaotic" drug problem, per this sketch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.85,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\rOriginal Text}We... did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.63,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可能範圍太大了\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, that's probably too big a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.68,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,謝琳\N{\rOriginal Text}Sherleen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:57.16,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,這些妓女有常光顧的毒販嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}was there a drug dealer the other hos favored?
