Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.21,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,模擬陪審團怎麼樣\N{\rOriginal Text}How'd the mock jury go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.91,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,很有用\N{\rOriginal Text}Useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.08,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,但不幸的是 他們對雷蒙德證詞的\N{\rOriginal Text}But, unfortunately, we got a pretty mixed reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.48,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,反應不一 所以我不能讓他上庭\N{\rOriginal Text}to Raymond's testimony, so I cannot put him on the stand.
