Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.13,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,可她不是很樂意\N{\rOriginal Text}which she is not excited about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:19.31,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,有個好消息\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, you're gonna like this.
