Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.71,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,曾經給所有女生供貨\N{\rOriginal Text}who used to supply all the girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.23,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,所以我們查了一下\N{\rOriginal Text}so we did a little digging,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.54,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,他的真名叫文森特·德盧卡\N{\rOriginal Text}and his real name is Vincent De Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.59,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,現在在伊文戴爾監獄 我們打算\N{\rOriginal Text}In prison at Evandale. We're gonna go up
