Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.20,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.85,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,終於有好消息了\N{\rOriginal Text}Some good news... finally.
