Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.39,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,特別是感恩節到了\N{\rOriginal Text}Over Thanksgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.87,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,好 沒問題\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.31,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rOriginal Text}Great.
