Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.50,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,就像你說的\N{\rOriginal Text}just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.85,Translated Text,,0,0,0,,今晚我得帶孩子\N{\rOriginal Text}I've got the kids tonight,
